[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m456[0m[39m:                           DNS_TYPE_AAAA, hostname, data->set.str[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mSTRING_DOH[0m[1;39m][0m[39m,[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m457[0m[39m:                           data->multi, dohp->req_hds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m458[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresult[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m459[0m[39m:      goto error;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m460[0m[39m:    dohp->pending++;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m461[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m462[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m463[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m464[0m[39m:#ifdef USE_HTTPSRR[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m465[0m[39m:  [0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m466[0m[39m:   * TODO: Figure out the conditions under which we want to make[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m467[0m[39m:   * a request for an HTTPS RR when we are not doing ECH. For now,[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m468[0m[39m:   * making this request breaks a bunch of DoH tests, e.g. test2100,[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m469[0m[39m:   * where the additional request does not match the pre-cooked data[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m470[0m[39m:   * files, so there is a bit of work attached to making the request[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m471[0m[39m:   * in a non-ECH use-case. For the present, we will only make the[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m472[0m[39m:   * request when ECH is enabled in the build and is being used for[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m473[0m[39m:   * the curl operation.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m474[0m[39m:   *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m475[0m[39m:# ifdef USE_ECH[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m476[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->set.tls_ech & CURLECH_ENABLE[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m477[0m[39m:     || data->set.tls_ech & CURLECH_HARD[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m478[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mport == [0m[1;36m443[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m479[0m[39m:      qname = [0m[1;35mstrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhostname[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m480[0m[39m:    else[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/transfer.[0m[1;92mc:180[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m260[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->conn->sockfd == CURL_SOCKET_BAD[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m181[0m[39m:    return CURLE_FAILED_INIT;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m182[0m[39m:  sockindex = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->conn->sockfd == data->conn->sock[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mSECONDARYSOCKET[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m183[0m[39m:  return [0m[1;35mCurl_shutdown_started[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, sockindex[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m184[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m185[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m186:C[0m[39mURLcode [0m[1;35mCurl_xfer_send_shutdown[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct Curl_easy *data, bool *done[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m187[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m188[0m[39m:  int sockindex;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m189[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!data || !data->conn[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:    return CURLE_FAILED_INIT;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->conn->writesockfd == CURL_SOCKET_BAD[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:    return CURLE_FAILED_INIT;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:  sockindex = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->conn->writesockfd == data->conn->sock[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mSECONDARYSOCKET[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:  return [0m[1;35mCurl_conn_shutdown[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, sockindex, done[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m: * Receive raw response data for the transfer.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m: * @param data         the transfer[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m201[0m[39m: * @param buf          buffer to keep response data received[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m: * @param blen         length of `buf`[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m: * @param eos_reliable if EOS detection in underlying connection is reliable[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m: * @param err error    code in case of [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m return[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m: * @return number of bytes read or [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m for error[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m: *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:static ssize_t [0m[1;35mxfer_recv_resp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct Curl_easy *data,[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m:                              char *buf, size_t blen,[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m209[0m[39m:                              bool eos_reliable,[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:                              CURLcode *err[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:  ssize_t nread;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mDEBUGASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mblen > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:  [0m[35m/[0m[39m* If we are reading BODY data and the connection does NOT handle EOF[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:   * and we know the size of the BODY data, limit the read amount *[0m[35m/[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m217[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!eos_reliable && !data->req.header && data->req.size != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m218[0m[39m:    curl_off_t totalleft = data->req.size - data->req.bytecount;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m219[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotalleft <= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m220[0m[39m:      blen = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m221[0m[39m:    else [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotalleft < [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcurl_off_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mblen[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m222[0m[39m:      blen = [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mtotalleft;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m223[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m224[0m[39m:  else [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mxfer_recv_shutdown_started[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m225[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* we already received everything. Do not try more. *[0m[35m/[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m226[0m[39m:    blen = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m227[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m228[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m229[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!blen[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m230[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* want nothing more *[0m[35m/[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m231[0m[39m:    *err = CURLE_OK;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m232[0m[39m:    nread = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m233[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m234[0m[39m:  else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m235[0m[39m:    *err = [0m[1;35mCurl_xfer_recv[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, buf, blen, &nread[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m237[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m238[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*err[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m239[0m[39m:    return [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m240[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnread == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m241[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->req.shutdown[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m242[0m[39m:      bool done;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m243[0m[39m:      *err = [0m[1;35mxfer_recv_shutdown[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, &done[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m244[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*err[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m245[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m246[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!done[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m247[0m[39m:        *err = CURLE_AGAIN;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m248[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m249[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m250[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m251[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mDEBUGF[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35minfof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, [0m[32m"sendrecv_dl: we are done"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m252[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m253[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mDEBUGASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnread >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m254[0m[39m:  return nread;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m255[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m256[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m257[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m*[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m258[0m[39m: * Go ahead and do a read if we have a readable socket or if[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m259[0m[39m: * the stream was rewound [0m[1;39m([0m[39min which case we have data in a[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m260[0m[39m: * buffer[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/doh.h:[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m85[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m159[0m[39m:  return TRUE;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:static CURLcode [0m[1;35mxfer_recv_shutdown[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct Curl_easy *data, bool *done[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:  int sockindex;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m166[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!data || !data->conn[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m167[0m[39m:    return CURLE_FAILED_INIT;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m168[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->conn->sockfd == CURL_SOCKET_BAD[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m169[0m[39m:    return CURLE_FAILED_INIT;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m170[0m[39m:  sockindex = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->conn->sockfd == data->conn->sock[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mSECONDARYSOCKET[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:  return [0m[1;35mCurl_conn_shutdown[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, sockindex, done[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:static bool [0m[1;35mxfer_recv_shutdown_started[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct Curl_easy *data[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m176[0m[39m:  int sockindex;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m177[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m178[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!data || !data->conn[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m179[0m[39m:    return CURLE_FAILED_INIT;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m180[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->conn->sockfd == CURL_SOCKET_BAD[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/doh.[0m[1;92mc:1388[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1395[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1388[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1389[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1390[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1391[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* All done *[0m[35m/[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1392[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1393[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1394[0m[39m:    return result;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1395[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/request.[0m[1;92mc:102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m110[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mreq;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!aborted[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mreq_flush[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:#ifndef CURL_DISABLE_DOH[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:  return CURLE_OK;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/request.[0m[1;92mc:119[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m127[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_safefree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mreq->p.ftp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_safefree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mreq->newurl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m122[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mreq->sendbuf_init[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m123[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mCurl_bufq_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&req->sendbuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m124[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m125[0m[39m:#ifndef CURL_DISABLE_DOH[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m126[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m127[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Identify and confirm the root cause:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash happens in Curl_doh_close at the line “mid = [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdoh->probe[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mslot[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.easy_mid;” because the entire DNS-over-HTTPS context [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`data->req.doh`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is still live [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnon-NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and gets torn down inside [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCurl_doh_cleanup, then later gets torn down *again* via the patched calls in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`lib/request.c`.  After the first cleanup [0m[1;39m([0m[39min doh.c, when a DOH resolution [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompletes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, `data->req.doh` is freed and set to NULL by `Curl_safefree`; but [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecause `Curl_client_reset` in `Curl_req_done` does not clear the `data->req.doh` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfield, the second call to `Curl_doh_cleanup` in `Curl_req_done` sees a stale [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon-NULL pointer and attempts to access and free it again.  That [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdouble-free/double-use‐after-free leads to a wild read in the subsequent call to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Curl_doh_close`.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Preservation of existing functionality:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must still clean up DOH handles when they have outstanding probes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginal call in doh.c does that[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We must still tear down any leftover DOH context at the end of a transfer, but[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly if it hasn’t already been cleaned up.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Proposed patch steps:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In lib/doh.c, *remove* the unconditional call to `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe end of the DOH resolution function [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Curl_doh`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and instead rely on the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransfer cleanup path [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Curl_req_done`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to always free the DOH context exactly [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monce.  That means in doh.c, change:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-     [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return result;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      …[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      to simply:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return result;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This prevents freeing the DOH context twice [0m[1;39m([0m[39monce inside Curl_doh and once at[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransfer-done[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. In lib/request.c, restore the original call path: keep `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the per-request cleanup [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot `Curl_doh_cleanup`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and let `Curl_doh_cleanup` be [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalled exactly once at that point:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```diff[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      --- a/lib/request.c[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      +++ b/lib/request.c[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      @@ [0m[1;36m-102[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m102[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m @@ [0m[1;35mCurl_req_done[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct Curl_easy *data[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mreq_flush[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      #ifndef CURL_DISABLE_DOH[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      -  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      +  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* only close any outstanding probes *[0m[35m/[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      #endif[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return CURLE_OK;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      …[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      @@ [0m[1;36m-120[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m +[0m[1;36m120[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m7[0m[39m @@ [0m[1;35mCurl_request_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct Curl_easy *data[0m[1;39m)[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mCurl_bufq_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&req->sendbuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      #ifndef CURL_DISABLE_DOH[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      -  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      +  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      #endif[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         req->size = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      ```[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. Immediately *after* the loop that closes individual probes in [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, add a single free of the DOH context if and only if all probes [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhave been closed [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `[0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoh && doh->pending == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcurl_slist_free_all[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoh->req_hds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[1;35mCurl_safefree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->req.doh[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  In other [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwords, fold the cleanup into the “close” function so that `Curl_doh_cleanup` is no [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlonger needed [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor becomes a thin wrapper that calls `Curl_doh_close`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - That change centralizes the free logic, ensuring it only runs once, after [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall handles have been removed and closed.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Removing the early cleanup in `Curl_doh` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`lib/doh.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m prevents a [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muse-after-free when the transfer cleanup runs.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Restoring the original `Curl_doh_close` invocation in `lib/request.c` [0m[1;39m([0m[39minstead[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof `Curl_doh_cleanup`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m maintains the semantics: “first close per-probe easy [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandles, then free the DOH context.”[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Consolidating “close” + “cleanup” into a single function prevents accidental [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdouble cleanup from two call sites.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side-effects and mitigation:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This patch ensures the DOH context lives through the entire transfer, only [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mgets freed once, and avoids both memory leaks and double-frees.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It preserves existing multi-handle cleanup logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39mremoving and closing each [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39measy handle[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, only moving the `curl_slist_free_all` and `[0m[1;35mfree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->req.doh[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing tests and harness code are unaffected: we have not modified any [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness, fuzzing logic, or external utilities.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We should add a small unit test to ensure that `data->req.doh` becomes NULL [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter request completion and that no double-free occurs when both `Curl_doh` and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Curl_req_done` paths are exercised.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>lib/doh.[0m[1;92mc:1388[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1395[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>lib/request.[0m[1;92mc:102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m110[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>lib/request.[0m[1;92mc:119[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m127[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After rebuilding and running the same fuzzing command, AddressSanitizer reports:[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    SEGV in `Curl_doh_close [0m[35m/src/curl/lib/[0m[95mdoh.c[0m[39m:[0m[1;92m1409:30[0m[39m`  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Backtrace again through `Curl_req_done` → `multi_done` → … → main.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The failure remains identical in location and nature [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwild read[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo obtain a holistic view of the fault chain, the following areas should be [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexamined:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Memory ownership and lifetime of the `doh_probes` structure:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How and when `data->req.doh` is allocated, initialized, and freed.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Validity of `doh->req_hds` and other members at the time `Curl_doh_close` is [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalled.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. `Curl_doh_close` implementation [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`lib/doh.c`, around line [0m[1;36m1409[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Which pointers it dereferences and under what conditions.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Differences in code paths when `dohp->pending` is true or false.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Callers in the multi-interface:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `Curl_req_done` and `multi_done` in `lib/request.c` and `lib/multi.c`.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether they guarantee proper setup of DoH state before invoking cleanup.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Interaction with the HTTP fuzzer harness:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How test inputs steer execution into DoH code paths.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Whether any sandboxing or partial initialization leads to uninitialized or [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfreed pointers.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBy tracing allocation, initialization, and cleanup across these components, it will[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe possible to map out the invalid pointer use in `Curl_doh_close`.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
