[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m231[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35minfof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoh, [0m[32m"DoH request %s"[0m[39m, [0m[1;35mcurl_easy_strerror[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresult[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m232[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m233[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!dohp->pending[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m234[0m[39m:      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* DoH completed, run the transfer picking up the results *[0m[35m/[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m235[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mCurl_expire[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, EXPIRE_RUN_NOW[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m236[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m237[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m238[0m[39m:  return [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m239[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/request.[0m[1;92mc:100[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m110[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m100:C[0m[39mURLcode [0m[1;35mCurl_req_done[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct SingleRequest *req,[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:                       struct Curl_easy *data, bool aborted[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mreq;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!aborted[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mreq_flush[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:#ifndef CURL_DISABLE_DOH[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:  return CURLE_OK;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/doh.[0m[1;92mc:1390[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1395[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1390[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1391[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* All done *[0m[35m/[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1392[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1393[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1394[0m[39m:    return result;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1395[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/request.[0m[1;92mc:102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m110[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mreq;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!aborted[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m([0m[39mvoid[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35mreq_flush[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:#ifndef CURL_DISABLE_DOH[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m109[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m110[0m[39m:  return CURLE_OK;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlib/request.[0m[1;92mc:113[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m121[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m113[0m[39m:void [0m[1;35mCurl_req_hard_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct SingleRequest *req, struct Curl_easy *data[0m[1;39m)[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m114[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m115[0m[39m:  struct curltime t0 = [0m[1;39m{[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m116[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m117[0m[39m:  [0m[35m/[0m[39m* This is a bit ugly. `req->p` is a union and we assume we can[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m118[0m[39m:   * free this safely without leaks. *[0m[35m/[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m119[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_safefree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mreq->p.ftp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m120[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_safefree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mreq->newurl[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m121[0m[39m:  [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Revert the unintended removal of the synchronous‐path cleanup in lib/doh.c:[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the “non-pending” branch of Curl_doh [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m1391[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, restore the call [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m after [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. This ensures that code path [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremains symmetrical with the error path and frees data->req.doh immediately when [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDoH resolution completes synchronously.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Ensure that the DoH state [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct doh_probes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is freed and reset at the end of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m*every* transfer, not just the synchronous branch:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In lib/request.c, locate the two places where [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is invoked [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munconditionally:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a. In Curl_req_done [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m107[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m109[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b. In Curl_req_hard_reset [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m125[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m127[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace those calls to [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCurl_doh_cleanup first invokes Curl_doh_close [0m[1;39m([0m[39msafely no‐op if probes are gone[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthen frees and NULLs data->req.doh, preventing stale probe metadata from surviving [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39macross transfers.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Leave Curl_req_free untouched: it already calls [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwill no‐op if data->req.doh is NULL.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Rationale:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By freeing and NULL‐setting data->req.doh in the async‐completion paths [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mCurl_req_done and Curl_req_hard_reset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, we guarantee that every new DoH invocation[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstarts with a freshly calloc’ed doh_probes struct whose .probe[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m.easy_mid entries [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare initialized to −[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. This eliminates any “wild‐addr‐read” stemming from iterating[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mover stale or uninitialized easy_mid values in Curl_doh_close.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Restoring the original cleanup call in the synchronous branch ensures symmetry[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith the error path and avoids any memory leak or double‐free [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCurl_safefree guards[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst freeing NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This preserves existing multi‐handle and fuzzer logic: we are not modifying [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness code, tests, or external libraries. We only change cleanup semantics within[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcurl’s request lifecycle.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Potential side effects are minimal: DoH state is now freed at the end of each [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtransfer instead of lingering until the easy handle is destroyed. This may slightly[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malter the memory‐retention profile for long‐lived connections, but functionally it [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatches the intended behavior of tearing down probe state after each request.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. References to similar code:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The error‐path in Curl_doh [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgoto error:[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m already uses Curl_doh_cleanup to free[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpartial allocations. We align the async‐path to the same pattern.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Curl_req_free’s use of Curl_doh_cleanup demonstrates that cleanup is safe to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall multiple times.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCode ranges to patch:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>lib/doh.[0m[1;92mc:1390[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1395[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>lib/request.[0m[1;92mc:102[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m110[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>lib/request.[0m[1;92mc:113[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m121[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImplementation outline [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno full diffs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In lib/doh.c:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* All done *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+   [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return result;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In lib/request.c, for Curl_req_done:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+ [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  return CURLE_OK;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In lib/request.c, for Curl_req_hard_reset:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;35mCurl_client_reset[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAn AddressSanitizer-driven libFuzzer run on the `curl_fuzzer_http` fuzzer exposed a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrash in `Curl_doh_close` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `lib/doh.[0m[1;92mc:1410[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m due to a wild read of memory. The [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muser attempted to mitigate the crash by changing two calls to [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `lib/request.c` to `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. After [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrebuilding and re-running the fuzzer, the same SEGV still occurs in [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Curl_doh_close`, now called from inside `Curl_doh_cleanup`.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack trace [0m[1;39m([0m[39mexcerpt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `Curl_doh_close [0m[35m/src/curl/lib/[0m[95mdoh.c[0m[39m:[0m[1;92m1410:30[0m[39m`  [0m                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`curl_multi_perform` → `fuzz_handle_transfer`  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash occurs on every run of the fuzzer input, suggesting a reproducible [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory-access problem inside the DoH cleanup code.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Observations  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The invalid read originates in `Curl_doh_close` within `doh.c`.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash is not in the fuzzer harness itself but in the core cURL code under [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtest.  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The sanitizer reports a “wild-addr-read,” hinting at an uninitialized or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready-freed pointer being dereferenced.[0m                                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Two locations where `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` was called were changed to [0m        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      #ifndef CURL_DISABLE_DOH[0m                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1348[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresult[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1349[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1350[0m[39m:        return result;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1351[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1352[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1353[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->share[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1354[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mCurl_share_lock[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, CURL_LOCK_DATA_DNS, CURL_LOCK_ACCESS_SINGLE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1355[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1356[0m[39m:      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* we got a response, store it in the cache *[0m[35m/[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1357[0m[39m:      dns = [0m[1;35mCurl_cache_addr[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, ai, dohp->host, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, dohp->port, FALSE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1358[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1359[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata->share[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1360[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mCurl_share_unlock[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, CURL_LOCK_DATA_DNS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1361[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1362[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39m!dns[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1363[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[39m* returned failure, bail out nicely *[0m[35m/[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1364[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mCurl_freeaddrinfo[0m[1;39m([0m[39mai[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1365[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1366[0m[39m:      else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1367[0m[39m:        data->state.async.dns = dns;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1368[0m[39m:        *dnsp = dns;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1369[0m[39m:        result = CURLE_OK;      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* address resolution OK *[0m[35m/[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1370[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1371[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m* address processing done *[0m[35m/[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1372[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1373[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Now process any build-specific attributes retrieved from DNS *[0m[35m/[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1374[0m[39m:#ifdef USE_HTTPSRR[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1375[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mde.numhttps_rrs > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && result == CURLE_OK && *dnsp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1376[0m[39m:      struct Curl_https_rrinfo *hrr = NULL;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1377[0m[39m:      result = [0m[1;35mdoh_resp_decode_httpsrr[0m[1;39m([0m[39mde.https_rrs->val, de.https_rrs->len,[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1378[0m[39m:                                       &hrr[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1379[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mif[0m[1;39m([0m[39mresult[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1380[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35minfof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, [0m[32m"Failed to decode HTTPS RR"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1381[0m[39m:        return result;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1382[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1383[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35minfof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, [0m[32m"Some HTTPS RR to process"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1384[0m[39m:# ifdef DEBUGBUILD[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1385[0m[39m:      [0m[1;35mdoh_print_httpsrr[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata, hrr[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1386[0m[39m:# endif[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1387[0m[39m:      [0m[1;39m([0m[39m*dnsp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m->hinfo = hrr;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1388[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1389[0m[39m:#endif[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1390[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1391[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* All done *[0m[35m/[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1392[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1393[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1394[0m[39m:    return result;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1395[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1396[0m[39m:  [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m [0m[35m/[0m[39m* !dohp->pending *[0m[35m/[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1397[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1398[0m[39m:  [0m[35m/[0m[39m* else wait for pending DoH transactions to complete *[0m[35m/[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1399[0m[39m:  return CURLE_OK;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1400[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash arises because `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_is_resolved[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` immediately after decoding DoH responses. That frees [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`data->req.doh` while the transfer is still in progress.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Later, `[0m[1;35mCurl_req_done[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand even the user’s attempted patch to call [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Curl_doh_cleanup` there[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m invokes `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, which dereferences the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malready-freed `data->req.doh`, leading to a wild read.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - There are two valid cleanup points for the DoH state:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Detach outstanding DoH transfers via `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at request [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompletion, preserving the `doh_probes` struct for final teardown.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Free the `doh_probes` struct and associated header list exactly once in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCurl_req_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` via `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Prematurely freeing the struct inside `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_is_resolved[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` violates that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlifecycle, causing the crash.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Proposed Fix[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Revert the last patch in `lib/request.c` that replaced `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. Leave the request-end logic to call only [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In `lib/doh.c`, remove the premature `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` invocation in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_is_resolved[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m1393[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. That is, after[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      do **not** free `data->req.doh` there; simply return the result. The final [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcleanup remains in `[0m[1;35mCurl_req_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Ensure no other code paths call `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` before [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mCurl_req_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Steps[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In lib/request.c:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Restore `[0m[1;35mCurl_req_done[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to call `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Leave `[0m[1;35mCurl_req_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` unchanged so it calls `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` once.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In lib/doh.c:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Locate `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_is_resolved[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at lines ~[0m[1;36m1391[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m1395[0m[39m.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Delete [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor comment out[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m the line `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` right before [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`return result;`.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Retain the preceding call to `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdata[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mused to detach probes[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand the `[0m[1;35mde_cleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[39m&de[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` call.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This approach preserves the correct two-phase cleanup of DoH state:[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Detach outstanding handles [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Curl_doh_close`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m as soon as resolution is [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdone.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Free the state [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Curl_doh_cleanup`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m only at ultimate request teardown in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Curl_req_free`.[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It removes the double-free/free-use scenario without altering the intended [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic for closing probes or leaking memory.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing tests and harness logic remain valid: fuzz targets still hit the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame code paths, but without the wild memory access.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar patterns elsewhere in cURL ensure that resource cleanup happens at the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mend of a transfer, not mid-stream.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Side-Effects & Mitigation[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No memory leak is introduced because the `doh_probes` struct and its header [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlist are still freed exactly once in `[0m[1;35mCurl_req_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - There is a minor behavioral change: after DoH resolution, the state object [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpersists until request teardown. This matches the multi-interface’s design for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpipelining and reuse.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - If any custom code path expected the DoH struct to be freed immediately after [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresolution, adjust that code to instead rely on `[0m[1;35mCurl_doh_close[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` only and let the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstandard teardown handle full cleanup.[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. References & Context[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The two cleanup calls in question are in:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `lib/doh.c: [0m[1;35mCurl_doh_is_resolved[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpremature cleanup[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `lib/request.c: [0m[1;35mCurl_req_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mCurl_req_done[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcorrect cleanup [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpoints[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to harness or test code are necessary.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This fixes the AddressSanitizer “wild-addr-read” by ensuring the memory [0m       [2m                [0m
